<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LOG.GG - 롤 챔피언 정보</title>
    <style>
        /* 기존 스타일 그대로 유지 (수정 없음) */
        @import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css');

        :root {
            --primary-navy: #475569;
            --accent-blue: #3b82f6;
            --bg-soft: #f8fafc;
            --card-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            --container-width: 1440px;
            --sidebar-width: 280px;
        }

        html {
            /* 페이지 전체에 부드러운 스크롤 효과 적용 */
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        a{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-soft);
            color: #212529;
            width: var(--container-width);
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            background: var(--primary-navy);
            padding: 15px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            height: 40px;
        }

        .header-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ecf0f5;
        }

        .user-nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ecf0f5;
        }

        .btn-logout {
            padding: 8px 18px;
            background: var(--bg-soft);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 13px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .main-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: var(--sidebar-width) 1fr var(--sidebar-width);
            gap: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            min-height: 800px;
        }

        .content-area {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 38px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--primary-navy);
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }

        .top-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .search-bar {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            width: 380px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .search-bar:focus-within {
            border-color: var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .search-bar input {
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: var(--primary-navy);
        }

        .detail-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .hero-title::before {
            content: '•';
            color: var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .hero-info-top {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .hero-illust {
            width: 250px;
            height: 180px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .hero-desc-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .detail-tabs {
            display: flex;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            width: fit-content;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .d-tab {
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-right: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .d-tab:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .d-tab:hover,
        .d-tab.active {
            background: var(--accent-blue);
            color: white;
        }

        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .info-section h4 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .skill-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .skill-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .skill-item input {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
        }

        .skin-list {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .skin-box {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .comment-row {
            background: #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .comment-main {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .comment-side {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .side-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .side-card h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0 0 18px 0;
            color: var(--primary-navy);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .side-card h3::before {
            content: '';
            width: 4px;
            height: 16px;
            background: var(--accent-blue);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .menu-item {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-navy);
            padding: 10px 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .sub-item {
            padding: 8px 0 8px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .sub-item:hover {
            color: var(--accent-blue);
        }

        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="header-left">☰ 리그 오브 레전드 ▾</div>
        <div class="user-nav">
            <span>마이페이지</span>
            <span><b>USER01</b> 님</span>
            <button class="btn-logout">로그아웃</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="main-layout">
        <aside class="side-left">
            <div class="side-card">
                <h3>카테고리</h3>
                <div class="menu-item">갤러리</div>
                <div class="menu-item">게시판</div>
                <div class="sub-item">자유 게시판</div>
                <div class="sub-item">공략 게시판</div>
                <div class="menu-item">미디어</div>
                <div class="menu-item">1:1 문의</div>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main class="content-area">
            <div class="top-row">
                <div class="logo">LOG.GG</div>
                <div class="search-bar">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="챔피언 검색">
                    <span>🔍</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-card">
                <div class="hero-title">챔피언 이름 / 역할군</div>

                <div class="hero-info-top">
                    <div class="hero-illust">챔피언 일러스트</div>
                    <div class="hero-desc-text">
                        <div>챔피언 배경 이야기 및 소개</div>
                        <div>주요 포지션</div>
                        <div>난이도 / 공격 타입</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-tabs">
                    <div class="d-tab active">스킬</div>
                    <a href="#skin"><div class="d-tab">스킨</div></a>
                    <a href="#item"><div class="d-tab">룬 / 아이템</div></a>
                    <a href="#patch"><div class="d-tab">패치</div></a>
                </div>

                <div class="info-section" id="skill">
                    <h4>스킬 정보</h4>
                    <div class="skill-list">
                        <div class="skill-item"><input type="checkbox"> P (패시브) - 고유 능력</div>
                        <div class="skill-item"><input type="checkbox"> Q - 기본 스킬 1</div>
                        <div class="skill-item"><input type="checkbox"> W - 기본 스킬 2</div>
                        <div class="skill-item"><input type="checkbox"> E - 기본 스킬 3</div>
                        <div class="skill-item"><input type="checkbox"> R (궁극기) - 필살기</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-section" id="skin">
                    <h4>스킨 목록</h4>
                    <div class="skin-list">
                        <div class="skin-box"></div>
                        <div class="skin-box"></div>
                        <div class="skin-box"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-section" id="item">
                    <h4>추천 룬 / 아이템</h4>
                    <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8;">준비 중인 데이터입니다.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-section" id="patch">
                    <h4>최근 패치 내역</h4>
                    <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8;">해당 챔피언의 최근 변경 사항이 없습니다.</div>
                </div>

                <div class="comment-row">
                    <div>심해 탈출러 |</div>
                    <div class="comment-main">이 챔피언 이번 패치로 엄청 상향된 것 같아요!</div>
                    <div class="comment-side">
                        <span>| 신고 |</span>
                        <span>공감</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <aside class="side-right">
            <div class="side-card" style="background: #cbd5e1; height: 300px;">
                <h3>광고 및 로테이션</h3>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>

    <footer>© 2026 LOG.GG 롤 서비스. 모든 권리 보유.</footer>

    <script>
        const dTabs = document.querySelectorAll('.d-tab');
        dTabs.forEach(tab => {
            tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
                dTabs.forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
                tab.classList.add('active');
            });
        });
    </script>

</body>

</html>